The paper deals with signal processing and communication, which are typically covered under cs.SP (Signal Processing) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the complexity of reconstruction and support detection, which are related to cs.MM (Mathematical Methods) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The problem of sphere packing also has connections to cs.CG (Computational Geometry).
